If this card is Tributed by a card effect: You can add 1 Spellcaster-Type "Nekroz" Ritual Monster from your Deck to your hand. If this card is banished: You can send 1 "Nekroz" monster from your Deck to the Graveyard, except "Archmage of the Nekroz". You can only use 1 "Archmage of the Necloth" effect per turn, and only once that turn.
